text:
It seems that memprofiler is now Pyhon2.6 incompatible. We should drop the Python 2.6 support.

* [ ] Grep the code for "2.6" and change everything to 2.7 or remove
* [ ] Related: in nilearn/version.py, we should now use an OrderedDict
* [ ] switch travis
title: Drop Python 2.6 compatibility
